<paragraph id="2418850BFFEA8315FC975F04FE32FE96" blockId="87.[823,1475,1700,1948]" lastBlockId="88.[113,764,272,365]" lastPageId="88" lastPageNumber="88" pageId="87" pageNumber="87">
The species was transferred by 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFFEA831AFB585F3FFAEBF880" author="BORNMULLER, J." box="[1180,1403,1887,1915]" pageId="87" pageNumber="87" pagination="114 - 116" refId="ref136478" refString="BORNMULLER, J. (1906). Die Arten und Formen der persischen Cruciferengattungen Clastopus Bge. und Straussiella Hausskn. Repert. Spec. Nov. Regni Veg. 3: 114 - 116." type="journal article" year="1906">BORNMÜLLER (1906)</bibRefCitation>
to the monospecific 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFEA831AFC0B5FE4FBD4F867" authorityName="Haussknecht" authorityYear="1897" box="[975,1092,1924,1948]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Straussiella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="87" pageNumber="87" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="16D35919FFEA831AFC0B5FE4FBD4F867" box="[975,1092,1924,1948]" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="87">Straussiella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and remained there for more than a century. However, it is recently retained by 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFFE58315FDA75970FF25FEB6" author="SPANIEL, S. &amp; KEMPA, E. &amp; SALMERON-SANCHEZ, J. &amp; AGUILAR, J. F. &amp; MOTA, I. &amp; AL-SHEHBAZ, D. A. &amp; GERMAN, K. &amp; OLSAVSKA, B. &amp; SINGLIAROVA, K. &amp; K. MARHOLD" pageId="88" pageNumber="88" pagination="2463 - 2491" refId="ref143598" refString="SPANIEL, S., M. KEMPA, E. SALMERON-SANCHEZ, J. FUERTES- AGUILAR, J. F. MOTA, I. A. AL-SHEHBAZ, D. A. GERMAN, K. OLSAVSKA, B. SINGLIAROVA, K. ZOZOMOVA-LIHOVA &amp; K. MARHOLD (2015). AlyBase: database of names, chromosome numbers, and ploidy levels of Alysseae (Brassicaceae), with a new generic concept of the tribe. Pl. Syst. Evol. 301: 2463 - 2491." type="journal article" year="2015">ŠPANIEL et al. (2015)</bibRefCitation>
in 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFE58315FF1F5955FEACFEB6" box="[219,316,309,333]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Clastopus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="88" pageNumber="88" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="16D35919FFE58315FF1F5955FEACFEB6" box="[219,316,309,333]" italics="true" pageId="88" pageNumber="88">Clastopus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on molecular data and a closer reexamination of morphology.
</paragraph>
